      {{#> column-layout--default}}
        <h3 class="article_headline">Step 5. Position Summary</h3>
        <p>Having decided to buy, you have a trading position that is now long one unit of corn. (Selling would result in a short position.) Your position is reflected below the trading chart in the position summary. You'll notice that prices – as well as your unrealized profit and loss – update in real time in the summary. That way, if the market moves in your favor, you can simply click flatten to even your position and realize a profit.</p>
